{"tid":1971360,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點解決覺得同其他人既相處交流好無聊好無謂","createTime":"2020-04-14T00:26:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-14T05:21:32.000Z","uid":184722,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b5ac206997608cb9fa30642878eb2368bc4bf32b","tid":1971360,"uid":184722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T00:26:03.000Z","msg":"幾個月前識左個女仔<br />\n同佢都算好夾好傾<br />\n真係咩都有講下傾下<br />\n上至有關世界香港 <br />\n下至日常生活小事<br />\n<br />\n同唔係講完就算純9up<br />\n對話之間令我諗左好多野<br />\n睇好多野都唔同左<br />\n改變左我既生活習慣<br />\n<br />\n之後因為某d原因同佢既關係完左<br />\n但係之後無論我同朋友同事既相處<br />\n都覺得好無聊同好無謂好無營養<br />\n好似唔想再同其他人有任何交雜<br />\n<br />\n可以點解決......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49eb5a2000448b5aea77fc9c398c7246dca596a1","tid":1971360,"uid":6446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T00:27:55.000Z","msg":"點樣識？"},{"pid":"af93ad8180cd8b77f6b0616ae368923749c156ac","tid":1971360,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T00:29:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"517c975da73c8bcaf51b3debde61a15644e5bd42","tid":1971360,"uid":184722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49eb5a2000448b5aea77fc9c398c7246dca596a1","tid":1971360,"uid":6446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T00:27:55.000Z","msg":"點樣識？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T00:30:35.000Z","msg":"朋友的朋友"},{"pid":"91b6bf3f8e08104e0219317e7905b18cd7924a54","tid":1971360,"uid":184722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af93ad8180cd8b77f6b0616ae368923749c156ac","tid":1971360,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T00:29:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T00:30:59.000Z","msg":"我知難而退了"},{"pid":"36bc7eae427e96032e729